travelAgencyModel

Class Tour

  • java.lang.Object
    • travelAgencyModel.Travel
      • travelAgencyModel.Tour
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Tour
extends Travel
    Extension of Travel that adds departure, arrival and return dates as well as a CustomerList to keep track of the Customers associated with this Tour. Implements Serialization by extension.
    Author:
    DVN
    See Also:
